data.description: Investors!!! Current rental property for sale in quiet neighborhood. Currently rented for $1400.00/month. Remodeled brick home on a dead end street, with easy access to I-210 and McNeese. 3 bedroom, 2 bath with ceramic tile flooring throughout (no carpet), spacious rooms with ceiling fans, fresh paint in neutral color. Large privacy fenced backyard with a storage shed. Roof replaced in 2020. All measurements +/-. Currently occupied. Tenant requires 24 hour showing notice. No sign or lockbox on property. Flood Zone X
